    "An AI-powered thesaurus is used to suggest a list of potential synonyms.",
    "It can be integrated directly into Chrome and MS Word.During paraphrasing, it can compare outcomes and choose from eight predefined modes that help improve the fluency and readability of the text.Table 2 gives a detailed comparison between four writing and finishing tools.",
